Description :
  Unsurpassed realism and horror of the water element!
  The future holds many dangers. By 2051 people are faced with a new threat - the rapid growth of population and the flooding of fertile land. To solve this problem was created enormous scientific ship &quot;Queen of Peace&quot;, but this metropolis on the water has become a prime target for fanatics of extremists. Can you survive in fierce firefights and escape from a sinking ship, which has become a death trap?
  This is not a joke spooky action movie you have to break through the compartments and a huge deck liner, faced with relentless water element. On a sinking ship is no room for doubt - even a moment's hesitation could lead to a disaster. Only the desire to survive at any cost and the ability to use arms to help you avoid a painful death and disrupt the plans of nightmarish crazy fanatics.
